{"TopicId":17272,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Shadows","CreatedByName":"prot","CreatedById":5635,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-08-19T08:00:40Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"prot","CreatedById":5635,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-08-19T08:00:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHi!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIn the first place, sorry for my English.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI recently went through screenshots and realized that the shadows in the old version of KSP looked much better. Each part cast shadows on the rest of the ship. In the new version I don\u0027t see anything like that.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ehere\u0027s some examples:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://dl.dropbox.com/u/33017518/KSP/ksp_public/screenshot1.png\u0022 alt=\u0022screenshot1.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://dl.dropbox.com/u/33017518/KSP/ksp_public/screenshot4.png\u0022 alt=\u0022screenshot4.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://dl.dropbox.com/u/33017518/KSP/ksp_public/screenshot7.png\u0022 alt=\u0022screenshot7.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIs in the game settings influencing in this way the shadows? (I recently bought a new computer and set everything to full)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOr is it just a bug/feature?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ethanks\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Cykyrios","CreatedById":17639,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-08-19T08:16:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMaybe a screen of your graphics options would help, but I have no problem here, shadows are cast on the rocket.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI also have everything maxed, here\u0027s a little screenshot:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/SgxpF.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022SgxpF.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"prot","CreatedById":5635,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-08-19T08:41:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHere\u0027s my setting:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://dl.dropbox.com/u/33017518/KSP/ksp_public/settings.png\u0022 alt=\u0022settings.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eand another screen without shadows on ship :/\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://dl.dropbox.com/u/33017518/KSP/ksp_public/screenshot15.png\u0022 alt=\u0022screenshot15.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ebtw I have GF670 and latest drivers..\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"prot","CreatedById":5635,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-08-19T10:54:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI manage to find solution in this \u003Ca href=\u0022http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/showthread.php/15736-BUG-16-No-Shadows?highlight=cast\u002Bshadow\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ethread\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI had to change the registry: HKEY_CURRENT_USER/Software/Squad/Kerbal Space Program/UnityGraphicsQuality to 3\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E[spoiler=and I have shadows now \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E]\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022https://dl.dropbox.com/u/33017518/KSP/ksp_public/screenshot18.png\u0022 alt=\u0022screenshot18.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stoup","CreatedById":2804,"CreatedDateTime":"2012-08-19T10:58:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EDo you normally get shadows on the surface? I\u0027m not sure what causes it, but sometimes even with graphics settings cranked shadows simply don\u0027t show.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESee \u003Ca href=\u0022http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/showthread.php/15736-BUG-16-No-Shadows\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://kerbalspaceprogram.com/forum/showthread.php/15736-BUG-16-No-Shadows\u003C/a\u003E for a few more tips\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}